    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or a speck of dust out of place. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
