    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S is an investment-grade example of the 997.1 generation. Power is derived from the M97.01 3.8L flat-six, featuring VarioCam Plus and a dry-sump lubrication system, mated to a G97/01 6-speed manual transaxle. A verified DME report shows zero over-revs in ranges 3 through 6, confirming a lifetime of sympathetic operation. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip and turn-in precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless: no weeping from the rear main seal, zero bore scoring symptoms, and a perfectly pressurized cooling system. This is a turn-key, analog driver's car in collector-tier condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
